{
  "texts": [
    "Then, we introduce the optimization and inference stage of the proposed REFLECTOOL.",
    "The overview of the REFLECTOOL are shown in Figure 2.",
    "In this work, we focus on addressing clinicalrelated tasks with tool-use agents.",
    "The task is composed of X = {q, I} and y, where q is the instruction, I is the inputs with different formats, and y is the ground-truth answer.",
    "The agents are required to leverage the input information and complete the task in a multi-step manner."
  ]
}